.TH skill
.SH NAME
skill - client request for skill usage.
.SH DESCRIPTION
The skill request is used by the client to trigger skill usage for one of the objects
controlled by the client.
.br
Skill request contains ID and serial value of the object and ID of skill to use.
.SH JSON EXAMPLE
.nf
{
  "skill": [
    {
      "skill-id": "melee1",
      "object-id": "char1",
      "object-serial": "0"
    }
  ]
}
.SH SEE ALSO
response/error